*Day 2 Learning Focus

DOM Manipulation

Dynamic UI Updates using JavaScript

Working with Lists & Progress Bars

Beginner-level State Management

1️⃣ Problem Identified

Students often lose track of their daily study progress and fail to monitor subject-wise preparation, leading to poor time management and stress.

2️⃣ Solution Implemented

A Smart Study Tracker Dashboard that allows users to:

Add study subjects

Track progress visually

Stay motivated through progress feedback

3️⃣ Key Functionalities

Input subject name

Display subject list dynamically

Update study progress using buttons

Visual progress indicator using progress bars

Minimal UI with Black & Red theme

Technologies Used

HTML – Page structure

CSS – Styling and theme (Black + Red)

JavaScript – Logic, DOM updates, progress handling

5️⃣ Skills Learned

Accessing elements using getElementById

Creating elements dynamically using createElement

Updating UI based on user actions

Using arrays to store data

Real-Time Use Case

Useful for students preparing for:

Exams

Certifications

Daily study planning
